1.3
log
@Rename loadpoint to loadaddr and add to usage().

suggestion and ok from kettenis@@
@
text
@.\"     $OpenBSD: mkboot.8,v 1.2 2008/05/16 06:39:27 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2008 Mark Kettenis <kettenis@@openbsd.org>
